CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1956, pg. 16, reads: "Congratulations - Mr. and Mrs. Henry Price (left) receive congratulations from Mr. and Mrs. W. M. Haughery and tiny W. M. Haughery III at the reception which followed their wedding at Canaan Baptist Church. The bride is the former Josie Dae Pass. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mr. W. M. Haughery, and Mrs. Haughery holding baby W. M. Haughery III, with groom Henry Price, and bride Josie Dae Pass Price wearing light colored hat and light colored sheer elbow length fingerless gloves, posed in interior with floral curtains
